  "detailed_description": "<h1>Marriage Candidates</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/a6214cf6bb2c698e8858363613d81f4d.avif?t=1768456206\" width=800 height=707 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Violet Archive needs your help! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/d3ae87331dfc7c08a82be0ef7d2b052f.apng?t=1768456206\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/d3ae87331dfc7c08a82be0ef7d2b052f.poster.avif?t=1768456206\" class=\"bb_img\" width=106 height=30 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sightings of exotic plants and creatures near the town of Shimmerbrook have attracted a wave of new settlers. The Violet Archive was set up to record the development in the region, and is looking for researchers to aid its cause! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/626a0b36d3e7b8ba1125030d3fda6ecc.poster.avif?t=1768456206\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/626a0b36d3e7b8ba1125030d3fda6ecc.webm?t=1768456206\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/626a0b36d3e7b8ba1125030d3fda6ecc.mp4?t=1768456206\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/b1b6eb484ee2d54af249312c4d97ccc3.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> A game about research and discovery</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Discover and record 90+ </strong>plants, creatures, and fish at various locations around Shimmerbrook, and contribute your findings to the Archive.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/bfc669307406eb2bcbad21be0d289b46.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> Forage for seeds, grow crops with different growth conditions</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Observe wild plants </strong>and <strong>grow them as crops</strong> based on their requirements!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/72a269b2871a89d88889c333b9b4c97b.webp?t=1768456206\" width=20 height=26 /></span> Tame and raise 30 unique creatures! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/ee84b4d3b2eb632ef6453fffebf06a34.webp?t=1768456206\" width=20 height=26 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tame creatures as part of research</strong>! Observe wild creatures, learn their diet, and tame them with their favourite food!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Raise  creatures, meet their needs, and unlock their perks</strong>! Each creature has a unique ability: Chickens find you seeds, Sproutkittens grow seeds into sprouts instantly!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect Shimmers</strong>! These rare coloured variants give double the Produce!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/fd6e9496ec82205f2a28f41ca6422d12.apng?t=1768456206\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/fd6e9496ec82205f2a28f41ca6422d12.poster.avif?t=1768456206\" class=\"bb_img\" width=33 height=42 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/a958e0afe1c12bd110d2492a211d24ac.apng?t=1768456206\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/a958e0afe1c12bd110d2492a211d24ac.poster.avif?t=1768456206\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/aa0a25d623e60b785bdb3aa4cc1af7bd.apng?t=1768456206\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/aa0a25d623e60b785bdb3aa4cc1af7bd.poster.avif?t=1768456206\" class=\"bb_img\" width=54 height=27 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/b01930f2d756093841d15be08475f3ab.apng?t=1768456206\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/b01930f2d756093841d15be08475f3ab.poster.avif?t=1768456206\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/0a2aea61e880f837a4e81eeaabd2eb5f.apng?t=1768456206\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/0a2aea61e880f837a4e81eeaabd2eb5f.poster.avif?t=1768456206\" class=\"bb_img\" width=30 height=33 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/21a7a909e80f3bcca685c326b6a455b7.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> Fishing - some common fish, but also unique fish requiring research!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find</strong> <strong>Fish Parts</strong> and<strong> use different bait</strong> to hook various fish!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/c3960d40aede31bccdf58c810ff50fdc.avif?t=1768456206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras_big/c3960d40aede31bccdf58c810ff50fdc.avif?t=1768456206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/b6ffc4ee72fea15dc08fda1e349b9d9b.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> Dive deep into the Mines! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mine ores and gems</strong> in the Mines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Certain plants and creatures can be found only in the Mines!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/696631bcbaaa0436a6391022f5882d57.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span>Explore the puzzle caves to uncover the mystery behind Shimmerbrook</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete puzzles to obtain Artifacts</strong>! Each puzzle you solve brings you one step closer to learning the truth behind the proliferation of flora and fauna in Shimmerbrook.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/57cc5fbb9c982104ffa3a538d023705f.avif?t=1768456206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras_big/57cc5fbb9c982104ffa3a538d023705f.avif?t=1768456206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/f99239aad9f7d6643b43889acd5c46e6.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> Cook, craft, build, and more!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cook meals</strong> to gain buffs!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Craft and automate</strong> with sprinklers, auto-feeders, and more!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/62ad4dcdb8042e32a0e16bba4989c7e9.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> Meet the townsfolk!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Befriend townsfolk</strong>! From a druid whose family has lived for generations in the mountains, to a featherfolk whose first job is in this new town - many characters await in Shimmerbrook!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Schedule Hangout Events</strong> with them to learn more about their stories!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Romance</strong> any of the 10 romanceables and marry your favourite!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/8c66a7d57a38bc8504b40ee3e0a5cb39.avif?t=1768456206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras_big/8c66a7d57a38bc8504b40ee3e0a5cb39.avif?t=1768456206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/49d061f1ef1f548f76886bb3f0324445.avif?t=1768456206\" width=600 height=195 /></span></p>",
