3b43889acd5c46e6.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> Cook, craft, build, and more!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cook meals</strong> to gain buffs!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Craft and automate</strong> with sprinklers, auto-feeders, and more!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/62ad4dcdb8042e32a0e16bba4989c7e9.webp?t=1768456206\" width=22 height=22 /></span> Meet the townsfolk!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Befriend townsfolk</strong>! From a druid whose family has lived for generations in the mountains, to a featherfolk whose first job is in this new town - many characters await in Shimmerbrook!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Schedule Hangout Events</strong> with them to learn more about their stories!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Romance</strong> any of the 10 romanceables and marry your favourite!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/8c66a7d57a38bc8504b40ee3e0a5cb39.avif?t=1768456206\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras_big/8c66a7d57a38bc8504b40ee3e0a5cb39.avif?t=1768456206 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1629830/extras/49d061f1ef1f548f76886bb3f0324445.avif?t=1768456206\" width=600 height=195 /></span></p>",
